AMMAN, February 27 (Xinhua) -- The price index of Jordan's
Amman Financial Market closed at 159.41 points Sunday, exactly the
same points as Thursday's finish.
</P>
<P>
The turnover was 729,461 Jordanian dinars (some 1.02 million
U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
A total of 733,127 shares changed hands in 449 deals. 
