<HEADLINE> Pakistan Rejects Indian Claim on LoC Attack </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
"Pakistani troops are not involved in any such action and no
Pakistani soldier has gone across the Line of Control (LoC) and
such allegations seem to be part of Indian design to justify its
own activities of past LoC terrorism," state-run Pakistan
Television (PTV) said Sunday.
</P>
