<HEADLINE> Shenyin-Wanguo to Maintain Leading Status: New President </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
SHANGHAI, February 27 (Xinhua) -- Liu Mingkang, the new
president of the Shenyin-Wanguo Securities Co. Ltd., said here
today the brokerage will maintain its leading status among its
peers after China Everbright Bank became its largest shareholder.
</P>
