<DATE_TIME> 2000-02-27 </DATE_TIME>
<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Weekly Highlights of Chinese Science News (1) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
700-Year-Old City Site Unearthed in North China
</P>
<P>
The site of the nearly 700-year-old Zhongdu (Central Capital)
city was recently unearthed in north China's Shijiazhuang City,
after two years of excavations.
</P>
<P>
The construction of Zhongdu began in 1307 and was completed
four years later. Among the four capital cities of the Yuan
Dynasty (1271--1368), this is the only one that is still well
preserved.
</P>
<P>
Man Marks Five Years With Transplanted Lung
</P>
<P>
Ji Shuchun, a 52-year-old farmer, celebrated the fifth
anniversary of his lung transplant this week at Anzhen Hospital in
Beijing. Professor Chen Yuping with the hospital performed the
life-saving operation to transplant a new left lung into Ji in
February of 1995.
</P>
<P>
Yinhe III Super Computers Widely Used
</P>
<P>
Yinhe-III super computers, which have supplanted the Yinhe-II
model, are now widely used all over China.
</P>
<P>
Yinhe-III super computers were developed by National Defense
Science and Technology University based in Changsha, Hunan
Province.
</P>
<P>
Song Jian Elected Academician at NAE
</P>
<P>
Song Jian, president of the Chinese Academy of Engineering (CAE)
, has taken up an academic post at the National Academy of
Engineering (NAE) in the United States.
</P>
<P>
Song was elected for his contributions to aerospace engineering,
environmental protection, scientific and technology administration,
and fostering the international technical co-operation.
</P>
<P>
Rare Ancient Plant Grows Well in SW China
</P>
<P>
China has made a major breakthrough in breeding wild cycad, a
280-million-year-old rare plant species, over vast area of land.
</P>
<P>
A cycad forest covering 1,360 hectares has been created in the
suburbs of the city of Panzhihua in southwest China's Sichuan
Province, and the forest comprises 237,766 cycads, believed to be
the largest number of its kind in the world, said Yang Siyuan, a
horticulturist in Panzhihua.
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
